, you can get Spiritual Pet cards, Talisman cards and Guild Secret Spell cards. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">These cards are very rare, and their strength may be similar to the regular cards of the same rank, but they often bring you new building ideas and help you create unique and rare decks.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Battle with Other Players</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each of your opponents are other players online, and everyone builds a deck from scratch.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every battle with your opponent will test your deck’s strength, and you will be eliminated if you lose multiple battles.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Devise strategies, climb to the top of cultivation, and wait for you to battle!</p>",
